item.title: Just made a czar server and strugling making myself admin
item.dc:creator: @chassy13 Chassy13
item.description:
@chassy13 wrote:

Pj Owns, wrong. The command is right, but it makes all 100’s. Lol ;D :P[br][br][size=1]Posted on: February 16, 2008, 07:52:35 AM[/size][hr]Add this to your commands.

if (command.equalsIgnoreCase("starter")) { if (DGstarter == 0) { addItem(995, 1000000); // Adding items sendMessage("Your starter pack "+playerName, DGstarter += 1; saveGame(); } else if (DGstarter == 1) { sendMessage("All ready used your stater you greedy pig"); } }

if you want more items, just add under the addItem(995, 1000000); // Adding items, use the same thing they did except change the IDs
